<p class="p">Foaming capacity (FC) and foam stability (FS) of the proteins were determined using the modified methods of Lassissi et al. [
 <xref rid="B49-molecules-23-00393" ref-type="bibr" class="xref">49</xref>] and Liu et al. [
 <xref rid="B50-molecules-23-00393" ref-type="bibr" class="xref">50</xref>]. Protein samples (50 mg) were weighed and dispersed in 0.01 M phosphate buffer (10 mL) with a pH of 7.0 (
 <italic class="italic">V</italic>
 <sub class="sub">0</sub>). Then they were homogenized with an Ultra-Turrax T 25 (IKA-Labortechnik, Staufen, Germany) at 10,000 rpm for 2 min, poured into 50 mL graduated cylinders and the foam volume recorded at 0 min (
 <italic class="italic">V</italic>
 <sub class="sub">1</sub>) and 30 min (
 <italic class="italic">V</italic>
 <sub class="sub">2</sub>). FC and FS were calculated by the following Equation: 
 <disp-formula id="FD1-molecules-23-00393" class="disp-formula">
  <label class="label">(1)</label>
  <math id="mm1" class="math">
   <mrow class="mrow">
    <mrow class="mrow">
     <mi class="mi">F</mi>
     <mi class="mi">C</mi>
     <mo class="mo">=</mo>
     <mfrac class="mfrac">
      <mrow class="mrow">
       <msub class="msub">
        <mi class="mi">V</mi>
        <mn class="mn">1</mn>
       </msub>
       <mo class="mo">−</mo>
       <msub class="msub">
        <mi class="mi">V</mi>
        <mn class="mn">0</mn>
       </msub>
      </mrow>
      <mrow class="mrow">
       <msub class="msub">
        <mi class="mi">V</mi>
        <mn class="mn">0</mn>
       </msub>
      </mrow>
     </mfrac>
     <mo class="mo">×</mo>
     <mn class="mn">100</mn>
     <mo class="mo">%</mo>
    </mrow>
   </mrow>
  </math>
 </disp-formula>
 <disp-formula id="FD2-molecules-23-00393" class="disp-formula">
  <label class="label">(2)</label>
  <math id="mm2" class="math">
   <mrow class="mrow">
    <mrow class="mrow">
     <mi class="mi">F</mi>
     <mi class="mi">S</mi>
     <mo class="mo">=</mo>
     <mfrac class="mfrac">
      <mrow class="mrow">
       <msub class="msub">
        <mi class="mi">V</mi>
        <mn class="mn">2</mn>
       </msub>
       <mo class="mo">−</mo>
       <msub class="msub">
        <mi class="mi">V</mi>
        <mn class="mn">0</mn>
       </msub>
      </mrow>
      <mrow class="mrow">
       <msub class="msub">
        <mi class="mi">V</mi>
        <mn class="mn">0</mn>
       </msub>
      </mrow>
     </mfrac>
     <mo class="mo">×</mo>
     <mn class="mn">100</mn>
     <mo class="mo">%</mo>
    </mrow>
   </mrow>
  </math>
 </disp-formula>
</p>
